@startuml 09_transport_modes
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.8
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #f8fafc
skinparam participantBorderColor #94a3b8
skinparam participantBorderThickness 2
skinparam participantFontColor #1e3a5f
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #fefce8
skinparam noteBorderColor #f59e0b

title <size:18><color:#1d4ed8>**השוואת מצבי תחבורה**</color></size>\n<size:11><color:#64748b>RUDP+Sync  vs  TCP+Sync  vs  TCP+NoSync</color></size>

actor "👤 דפדפן" as browser #dbeafe

participant "nginx :80\n/ws → :8081\n/ws-tcp-sync → :8082\n/ws-tcp-nosync → :8083" as nginx #fffbeb

participant "ws_bridge.py\n:8081\nRUDP+Sync" as br_rudp  #f0fdf4
participant "ws_bridge_tcp.py\n:8082\nTCP+Sync"  as br_tcp_s #f0f9ff
participant "ws_bridge_tcp.py\n:8083\nTCP+NoSync" as br_tcp_n #fff1f2

participant "exam-server\n10.99.0.20-22\nRUDP :9000\nSYNC=1" as srv_rudp  #f0fdf4
participant "exam_server_tcp\n10.99.0.23\nTCP :9001\nSYNC=1"  as srv_tcp_s #f0f9ff
participant "exam_server_tcp\n10.99.0.24\nTCP :9001\nSYNC=0"  as srv_tcp_n #fff1f2

== מצב 1: RUDP + Sync (ברירת מחדל) ==

browser -> nginx    : GET /ws  Upgrade: websocket
nginx   -> br_rudp  : proxy_pass :8081
br_rudp -> srv_rudp : **RUDP/UDP** — sliding window\nheader 14B | CRC-16 | chunking | AIMD
srv_rudp --> br_rudp : **ZS wire** + server_sent_at_ms\nExamSendCoordinator stagger
br_rudp --> browser  : exam_resp\n+ sync proof (hold, target, transit)

note right of br_rudp #f0fdf4
  **✓ RUDP sliding window ARQ**
  **✓ ExamSendCoordinator stagger**
  **✓ Bridge self-correcting hold**
  spread < 10ms בין כל הלקוחות
end note

== מצב 2: TCP + Sync ==

browser -> nginx     : GET /ws-tcp-sync  Upgrade: websocket
nginx   -> br_tcp_s  : proxy_pass :8082
br_tcp_s -> srv_tcp_s : **TCP** — newline-delimited JSON\nwriter.write(json + b'\\n')
srv_tcp_s --> br_tcp_s : JSON + server_sent_at_ms\nExamSendCoordinator stagger
br_tcp_s --> browser  : exam_resp\n+ sync proof

note right of br_tcp_s #f0f9ff
  **✗ RUDP** (TCP handles reliability)
  **✓ ExamSendCoordinator stagger**
  **✓ Bridge hold**
  שימוש ל-השוואה: TCP vs RUDP
end note

== מצב 3: TCP + NoSync (Baseline) ==

browser -> nginx     : GET /ws-tcp-nosync  Upgrade: websocket
nginx   -> br_tcp_n  : proxy_pass :8083
br_tcp_n -> srv_tcp_n : **TCP** — newline-delimited JSON
srv_tcp_n --> br_tcp_n : JSON — **ללא** server_sent_at_ms\nשליחה מיידית, אין stagger
br_tcp_n --> browser  : exam_resp\n**⚠ אין sync proof**

note right of br_tcp_n #fff1f2
  **✗ RUDP**
  **✗ ExamSendCoordinator**
  **✗ Bridge hold**
  Baseline — ללא סנכרון
  SyncProofCard מציג: "⚠ Sync disabled"
end note

== בחירת מצב בדפדפן ==

note over browser #f0f9ff
  **ModeSelector (boot screen):**
  ?mode=rudp-sync   → /ws
  ?mode=tcp-sync    → /ws-tcp-sync
  ?mode=tcp-nosync  → /ws-tcp-nosync

  ניתן לפתוח שלושה טאבים במקביל להשוואה חיה
end note

@enduml
